{"tid":1500773,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［極緊急］嶺南罷課要人呀！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-24T06:40:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T09:03:44.000Z","uid":30138,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"bf5d35f0f86adaa69b1613a3cd5533d8e19002fa","tid":1500773,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:40:57.000Z","msg":"元朗恐襲事件過咗而家一個月， 除咗淨係識射波比教育局， 學校仲做過啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上次鄭國漢口口聲聲應承同學話會盡快召開校董會特別會議，而家又走數。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一昧譴責暴力，但對何君堯公然支持白衣暴徒、死亡恐嚇異見者視若無睹。依D唔係虛偽，唔係雙重標準係乜嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呢個時刻，校方竟然對於極權殘害香港市民、甚至係自己嘅學生嘅情況下仍然無動於衷，更加對被指涉及元朗恐襲既敗類校董何君堯一再姑息！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n面對校方無為，極權打壓，我地只能自救。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTNQCND.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTNQCND.jpg&h=88e10dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港已失常，荒謬成日常。面對學校冇好好保護我哋，面對警暴，我哋已經冇辦法再正常咁樣想過我哋平時嘅生活，我地唔可以再扮冇野發生咁繼續上堂。<br />\n<br />\n我地希望一齊傾下同學對罷課既想法，例如罷課既形式、長度、手法。沒有大台、民主決策；然後一齊籌備，9月開學不開課。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cot0Z07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCot0Z07.jpg&h=41cc1439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n距離新學期只是剩下數日，時間好迫切。我地好想知道大家對罷課既意向，你既意見會影響到罷課搞唔搞得成/點搞，極重要！麻煩大家花少少時間填下佢，再share俾身邊既嶺南同學，搞唔搞到，睇大家喇！ <br />\n<br />\n罷課意向調查：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/DtNTDE5uJYM49cf8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FDtNTDE5uJYM49cf8A&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=437ce9ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/DtNTDE5uJYM49cf8A</a><br />\n<br />\n嶺南抗爭資訊發放：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/lingsulate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flingsulate&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLsRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=8ecd5302\" target=\"_blank\">t.me/lingsulate</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有仲有，其實除左罷課要人，籌備都要人，如果唔介意幫手，請pm我。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n團結克難光復嶺南</span></span>"},{"pid":"ba10cc83e8cba82efbae74273db4b6a26c30e43c","tid":1500773,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:42:32.000Z","msg":"罷佢老味"},{"pid":"d6a4c5edbc42368ceb7675736b9de55995940a1d","tid":1500773,"uid":35229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d297e928f6641b23763fe2b65023146d529f5c7","tid":1500773,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"推到全校見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3924057d793d15bc849a2c43a092da4747eb33fc","tid":1500773,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"推到全校見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e43eb5fdd549b3468935677c2538c1038ae6b85","tid":1500773,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:45:56.000Z","msg":"推到全校見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d8178c166f04ad35ccfc54deb40bc2f8b980cd","tid":1500773,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:47:34.000Z","msg":"推到全校見到<br />\n唔係我含撚都唔掂"},{"pid":"8361e9e971dca2e0016e1990cab328a348056550","tid":1500773,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:49:07.000Z","msg":"由每個系開始"},{"pid":"2f9c18ac625d3057aeb6dce0097607571cc663c1","tid":1500773,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8361e9e971dca2e0